<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.6.2">
<l>tuṅkārā ravatti raivantu lavatto ṭukaṭaluḷ</l>
<l>poṅkārā raviltu yilumpu ṉita rūrpōlum</l>
<l>ceṅkālaṉ ṉanti kaḻtaṇ paṇaiyil peṭaiyōṭum</l>
<l>koṅkārka malatta larilcē ruṅku ṟuṅkuṭiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Kuṟuṅkuṭi, where a red-legged swan joins with [his] mate</l>
<l>On a pollen-filled lotus blossom in a shimmering cool pond,</l>
<l>Is like the city of the pure one who sleeps on a huge, proud serpent in the sea,</l>
<l>Where rivers join when they spread, coming from high, full cascades.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
